snippet.title: Jinko Official Release Trailer | New Physics-Based Indie Game
snippet.description:
Jinko is a physics-based musical arcade game where balls fall to the rhythm, and your job is to keep them up! Fight against gravity and time across a variety of unique songs and levels, or challenge yourself in the arcade mode to see how your best score stacks up on the global leaderboard.

Play now on Steam!

#BeanJuiceStudios #IndieGame #Gaming
